columns.name: RECORD_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier for the adjudication record.

columns.name: CONTACT_DATE_REAL
columns.description: A unique contact date in decimal format. The integer portion of the number indicates the date of contact. The digits after the decimal distinguish different contacts on the same date and are unique for each contact on that date. For example, .00 is the first/only contact, .01 is the second contact, etc.

columns.name: CONTACT_DATE
columns.description: The date of this contact in calendar format.

columns.name: O_BIN_NUMBER
columns.description: Card Issuer ID or Bank ID Number used for network routing.

columns.name: O_VERSION_NUMBER
columns.description: Code uniquely identifying the transmission syntax and corresponding Data Dictionary.

columns.name: O_TRANS_CODE_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code identifying the type of transaction.

columns.name: O_TRANS_CODE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PRCSR_CTRL_NUM
columns.description: Processor control number assigned by the processor.

columns.name: O_SERV_PROV_QUAL_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code qualifying the 'Service Provider ID' (201-B1).

columns.name: O_SERV_PROV_QUAL_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_SERV_PROV_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier for the pharmacy or provider

columns.name: O_DATE_OF_SERV_DT
columns.description: Identifies date the prescription was filled or professional service rendered or subsequent payer began coverage following Part A expiration in a long-term care setting only.

columns.name: O_SOFTWARE_VENDOR
columns.description: Code indicating the type of dispensing dose.

columns.name: O_CARDHOLDER_ID
columns.description: Insurance ID assigned to the cardholder or identification number used by the plan.

columns.name: O_CARDHOLDER_FIRST
columns.description: The insurance cardholder's first name used by the plan (312-CC)

columns.name: O_CARDHOLDER_LAST
columns.description: The insurance cardholder's last name used by the plan (313-CD)

columns.name: O_HOME_PLAN
columns.description: The code identifying the Blue Cross or Blue Shield plan ID which shows where the member's coverage has been designated. Usually where the member lives or purchased their coverage.

columns.name: O_PLAN_ID
columns.description: Plan ID assigned by the processor to identify a set of parameters, benefit, or coverage criteria used to adjudicate a claim.

columns.name: O_ELIG_CLAR_CODE_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code indicating that the pharmacy is clarifying eligibility for a patient.

columns.name: O_ELIG_CLAR_CODE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_GROUP_ID
columns.description: Unique ID assigned to cardholder group or employer group.

columns.name: O_PERSON_CODE
columns.description: NCPDP code assigned to a specific person within a family.

columns.name: O_PAT_RELAT_CODE_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code indicating the gender of the individual.

columns.name: O_PAT_RELAT_CODE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_OTH_PAY_BIN_NUM
columns.description: The secondary, tertiary, etc. card issuer or bank ID number used for network routing.

columns.name: O_OTH_PAY_PRCSR_NUM
columns.description: The unique identifier of the secondary, tertiary, etc. payer to the processor.

columns.name: O_OTH_PAY_CARD_ID
columns.description: Unique cardholder ID for the member associated with the designated Payor

columns.name: O_OTH_PAY_GROUP_ID
columns.description: ID assigned to the cardholder group or employer group by the secondary, tertiary, etc. payer.

columns.name: O_MEDIGAP_ID
columns.description: Patient's ID assigned by the Medigap insurer.

columns.name: O_MEDICAID_IND_ID
columns.description: Two character State abbreviation indicating the state where Medicaid coverage exists

columns.name: O_MEDICAID_IND_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PROV_ASGN_IND_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code indicating whether the provider accepts assignment.

columns.name: O_PROV_ASGN_IND_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PARTD_QUAL_FAC_ID
columns.description: ID that indicates the patient resides in a facility that qualifies for the CMS Part D benefit.

columns.name: O_PARTD_QUAL_FAC_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_MEDICAID_ID_NUM
columns.description: A unique member identification number assigned by the Medicaid Agency.

columns.name: O_MEDICAID_ASGN_NUM
columns.description: Number assigned by processor to identify the individual Medicaid Agency or representative.

columns.name: O_PAT_ID_QUAL_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code qualifying the 'Patient ID' (332-CY).

columns.name: O_PAT_ID_QUAL_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PAT_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier assigned to the patient

columns.name: O_PAT_DOB_DT
columns.description: The birth date of the patient.

columns.name: O_PAT_SEX_CODE_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code indicating the gender of the individual.

columns.name: O_PAT_SEX_CODE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PAT_FIRST_NAME
columns.description: Patient's first name sent to the payer (310-CA)

columns.name: O_PAT_LAST_NAME
columns.description: Patient's last name sent to the payer (311-CB)

columns.name: O_PAT_STREET
columns.description: Patient free text street address (322-CM)

columns.name: O_PAT_CITY
columns.description: Free-form text for city name.

columns.name: O_PAT_STATE_ID
columns.description: Standard State/Province Code as defined by appropriate government agency.

columns.name: O_PAT_STATE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PAT_ZIP
columns.description: Patient postal code zone excluding punctuation and blanks (zip code for US) (325-CF)

columns.name: O_PAT_PHONE_NUM
columns.description: Ten-digit phone number of patient.

columns.name: O_PLACE_OF_SERV_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code identifying the place where a drug or service is dispensed or administered.

columns.name: O_PLACE_OF_SERV_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_EMPLOYER_ID
columns.description: Unique ID assigned to employer.

columns.name: O_SMOKER_CODE_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code indicating the patient as a smoker or non-smoker.

columns.name: O_SMOKER_CODE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PREG_INDICATOR_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code indicating the patient as pregnant or non-pregnant.

columns.name: O_PREG_INDICATOR_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PAT_EMAIL_ADDRESS
columns.description: The E-Mail address of the patient (member).

columns.name: O_PAT_RESIDENCE_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code identifying the patient's place of residence.

columns.name: O_PAT_RESIDENCE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_RX_REF_NUM_QL_ID
columns.description: This ID indicates the type of bill submitted.

columns.name: O_RX_REF_NUM_QL_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_RX_REF_NUM
columns.description: Reference number assigned by the provider for the dispensed product or service provided.

columns.name: O_PROD_ID_QUAL_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code qualifying the value in 'Product/Service ID' (407-D7).

columns.name: O_PROD_ID_QUAL_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PROD_ID
columns.description: Code indicating whether the provider accepts assignment.

columns.name: O_ASC_RX_REF_NUM
columns.description: Associated 'Prescription/Service Reference Number' (402-D2) for particular service.

columns.name: O_ASC_RX_SERV_DT
columns.description: Date of the 'Associated Prescription/Service Reference Number' (456-EN).

columns.name: O_QUANTITY_DISP
columns.description: Quantity dispensed in metric decimal units.

columns.name: O_FILL_NUM
columns.description: The code indicating whether the prescription is an original or a refill.

columns.name: O_DAYS_SUPPLY
columns.description: Estimated number of days the prescription will last.

columns.name: O_COMPOUND_CODE_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code indicating whether or not the prescription is a compound.

columns.name: O_COMPOUND_CODE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_DAW_ID
columns.description: Code indicating whether or not the prescriber's instructions regarding generic substitution were followed.

columns.name: O_DAW_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_DATE_WRITTEN_DT
columns.description: Date prescription was written.

columns.name: O_NUM_REFILLS_AUTH
columns.description: Number of refills authorized by the prescriber.

columns.name: O_RX_ORIGIN_CODE_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code indicating the origin of the prescription.

columns.name: O_RX_ORIGIN_CODE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_QTY_PRESCRIBED
columns.description: Amount prescribed in metric decimal units.

columns.name: O_OTH_CVG_CODE_ID
columns.description: Code indicating whether or not the patient has other insurance coverage.

columns.name: O_OTH_CVG_CODE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_SPEC_PACK_IND_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code identifying the type of transaction.

columns.name: O_SPEC_PACK_IND_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_ORIG_PRD_ID_QL_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code qualifying the value in 'Originally Prescribed Product/Service Code' (Field 445-EA).

columns.name: O_ORIG_PRD_ID_QL_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_ORIG_RX_PROD
columns.description: NCPDP code of the initially prescribed product or service.

columns.name: O_ORIG_RX_QUANTITY
columns.description: Initial prescribed amount in metric decimal units

columns.name: O_ALT_ID
columns.description: Unique personal ID used for controlled product reporting. ID can be that of the patient or the person picking up the prescription as required by the state.

columns.name: O_SCHED_RX_ID_NUM
columns.description: The serial number of the prescription form.

columns.name: O_UNIT_OF_MEAS_ID
columns.description: NCPDP standard product billing codes.

columns.name: O_UNIT_OF_MEAS_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_LEVEL_OF_SERV_ID
columns.description: Code indicating the type of service the provider supplied

columns.name: O_LEVEL_OF_SERV_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PRIOR_AUTH_TYP_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code qualifying the value in 'Product/Service ID' (407-D7).

columns.name: O_PRIOR_AUTH_TYP_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_PRIOR_AUTH_NUM
columns.description: Code clarifying the 'Prior Authorization Number Submitted' (462-EV) or benefit/plan exemption.

columns.name: O_INT_AUTH_TYP_ID
columns.description: ID indicating that authorization occurred for intermediary processing.

columns.name: O_INT_AUTH_TYP_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_INT_AUTH_ID
columns.description: ID indicating intermediary authorization occurred.

columns.name: O_DISP_STATUS_ID
columns.description: Code indicating the quantity dispensed is a partial fill or the completion of a partial fill. Used only in situations where inventory shortages do not allow the full quantity to be dispensed.

columns.name: O_DISP_STATUS_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_QTY_INT_TO_DISP
columns.description: Metric decimal quantity of medication that would be dispensed on original filling if inventory were available. Used in association with a 'P' or 'C' in  'Dispensing Status' (343-HD).

columns.name: O_DAYS_INT_TO_DISP
columns.description: Days supply for metric decimal quantity of medication that would be dispensed on original dispensing if inventory were available. Used in association with a 'P' or 'C' in 'Dispensing Status' (343-HD).

columns.name: O_DELAY_RSN_CODE_ID
columns.description: NCPDP code to specify the reason that submission of the transactions has been delayed.

columns.name: O_DELAY_RSN_CODE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_TX_REF_NUMBER
columns.description: A reference number assigned by the provider to each of the data records in the batch or real-time transactions. The purpose of this number is to facilitate the process of matching the transaction response to the transaction. The transaction reference number assigned should be returned in the response.

columns.name: O_PAT_ASGN_IND_ID
columns.description: Code which indicates a patient's choice on assignment of benefits.

columns.name: O_PAT_ASGN_IND_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_ROUTE_ADMIN_ID
columns.description: This is an override to the "default" route referenced for the product. For a multi-ingredient compound, it is the route of the complete compound mixture.

columns.name: O_ROUTE_ADMIN_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: O_COMPOUND_TYPE_ID
columns.description: Unique ID used to clarify the type of compound.

columns.name: O_COMPOUND_TYPE_ID_EXT_CODE_LST_NAME
columns.description: The name of the list value.

columns.name: CM_CT_OWNER_ID
columns.description: The Community ID (CID) of the instance that owns this contact. This is only populated if you use IntraConnect.
